    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are trapped in a shrine. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To get out, you must follow the rules. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rules: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Proceed if there are no anomalies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn back if you find an anomaly. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aim for the destination, Hachiman. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Walking Simulator Inspired by &quot;Hachiman Entrance&quot; </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;8 Hachiman Entrance&quot; is a walking simulator inspired by places like the 8th exit. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sound-based Anomalies </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some anomalies will require identification by sound. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Therefore, the use of speakers or headphones is recommended. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Horror Elements </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game contains some horror elements. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play Time </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expected playtime is between 20 to 60 minutes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Video Distribution Guidelines</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Individuals and organizations alike are allowed to upload and stream videos without prior permission.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monetization is permitted only when using the features provided by the video distribution platform.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We would appreciate it if you could include the game’s name in the video or stream title, and add a link to the official page or store page in the description.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We bear no responsibility for any damages that may occur as a result of uploading or streaming videos related to this game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >These guidelines are subject to change without prior notice.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Please report bugs here.&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
